提出抗告狀。（應\r\n附繕本）\r\n                                    書記官  黃雅青\r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　111 　年　　6 　　月　　27　　日","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TCDM/110%2c%e9%87%8d%e8%a8%b4%2c1772%2c20220627%2c5/pdf"},"JID":"TCDM,110,重訴,1772,20220627,5","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"重訴","JNO":"1772","JDATE":"20220627","JTITLE":"強盜等"}